snippet.title: Fatherhood | Trailer
snippet.description:
It's our game, Fatherhood, a PC atmospheric war survival indie game, about the ultimate sacrifice of a father in the midst of war...
How far would you go for someone you love... ?

Join our Discord server to get the demo:
https://discord.gg/ZxtEFQKZXv

To get more information, and subscribe to our newsletter, here's the website:
http://fatherhoodgame.com/
